reviews.text: Small restaurant, which serve porridge and some kinds of the Guangdong style.  You CAN try the fire Vermicelli roll with XO source.  It's spicy!

This is a very traditional regional place that sell porridge, turnip cake, noodles etc. (粥，粉仔，麺，腸粉). Excellent food and very reasonable price.  So for this visit I have 虾米腸-dried shrimp rice rolls and 艇仔粥-boat porridge.
the best congee shop in HK

Traditional house made noodle you can't find in other place in the area. Steam rice noodle roll is made in traditional way which is now rare in Hongkong. Traditional receipe, ingredients, and authentic taste.  Price is higher than average noodle bar but guaranteed quality in return. Highly recommend : 雞絲鮮牛河粉，豬膶腸粉，西洋菜燒骨陳腎粥
Very good. Yummy
